Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:37.05,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}私　恋をしてしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:42.10,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}ああ　瞬間風速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:48.77,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}旋風のときめきにさらわれて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.95,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}雲を飛ばす
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.44,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嵐の後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.47,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}透き通る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.52,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}光の粒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:09.46,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}混じり気のない思い　残るの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.91,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}二人でいると
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.10,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}胸が熱いね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:19.16,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}嘘の付けない君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.55,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}夢が破れて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.80,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}泡になっても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:27.95,ED2J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}後悔しない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:01.62,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}想一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.76,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}要一直注视着哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:08.70,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}摇曳着的爱之气象图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.17,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}两颗心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.67,0:19:13.46,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:17.60,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}憧憬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:32.33,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}哈　天空多么澄澈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:37.05,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}我　陷入恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:42.10,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}啊　瞬间风速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:48.77,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}被旋风扰动心神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.95,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}越上云端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:55.44,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}暴风雨之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:58.47,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}清澈而明净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:01.52,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}光的粒粒投影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:09.46,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}留下了　毫无瑕疵的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.91,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}只要两个人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.10,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}心中就充满温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:19.16,ED2C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(200,200)}喜欢不会撒谎的你
